{"tid":1977713,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗黃店內鬥事件證實咗一樣野","createTime":"2020-04-18T07:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T07:46:20.000Z","uid":76615,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"31c73d69ae24c279f214dc7d91fef87c9191da38","tid":1977713,"uid":76615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:21:00.000Z","msg":"再咁落去黃圈只會不攻自破，六月開始武鬥完一排靜落黎，咁快就因小事文鬥自己人。清者自清，你係黃嘅人地自然會感受到，依家咁樣屌黎屌去，幫襯既人只會好灰心。<br />\n<br />\n我地每個人都有獨立思想，要幫襯邊一間黃店我地會自己揀，你間野係好食嘅，自然會多人去。無論你間野有幾多打手，難食嘅話自然無咁多顧客。<br />\n<br />\n另外，對家一定有人係facebook分化我地，大家一定要分析清楚，唔好咁容量比人帶到風，你唔清楚既，唔好加把嘴落去。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只有團結，我地先可以壯大黃圈</span>"},{"pid":"0f5b6e5005a320ede727b2a23eeed1ca5178b8b2","tid":1977713,"uid":89349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:36:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200418/large/1587141530_0e44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200418%2Flarge%2F1587141530_0e44.jpg&h=5e1f1c81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警務人員子女關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1870807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1870807</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ea199dd5d5ddb05804eb0b05d130d795418414d2","tid":1977713,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:42:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b4548b8c9e85c4764659d6ec6c9242b7d023322","tid":1977713,"uid":41458,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:43:34.000Z","msg":"根本大部分人都冇內鬥<br />\n唔好當係連登上面帶風向嘅人係主流意見"},{"pid":"ee808dc6a3202ee2c868ccde2f6485befdee9712","tid":1977713,"uid":263618,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:46:09.000Z","msg":"救命我睇你啲Post都睇到煩<br />\n我都唔知係咩事因為所有同黃店有關嗰啲標題我都冇click入去睇, 因為九成九係分化post<br />\n由得佢沉啦"},{"pid":"82e3192de6b41609338ca2f3b78ad0dcca1751ec","tid":1977713,"uid":240890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b4548b8c9e85c4764659d6ec6c9242b7d023322","tid":1977713,"uid":41458,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:43:34.000Z","msg":"根本大部分人都冇內鬥<br />\n唔好當係連登上面帶風向嘅人係主流意見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T07:46:20.000Z","msg":"就算我上開連登<br />\n我都無追開呢單野<br />\n根本我就唔care <br />\n總之就照幫襯"}]}